{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d03f040997","title":"对军委关于军事系统向中央汇报工作问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25d73a33d5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"d03f040997"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"51c7140ed8","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央军委1957年2月22日关于军事系统各部门，各军种、兵种向党中央主席和中央政治局同志汇报工作问题给毛泽东的报告。报告说，军委经过讨论，初步预定：按总参、总政、总干、训练总监部、武装力量监察部、总后勤部、空军、海军、炮兵、装甲兵、通信兵、工程兵、铁道兵、防化学兵的次序，依次汇报，最好都能分别汇报一次，以便政治局同志多了解一些军队工作情况，多给些指示。但是否每个部门都一一汇报，或只抽其中几个重要部门和军种、兵种汇报，请指示。汇报时间可在3月20日至4月中旬以前。"}],"contents":[{"id":"50c8cdaacd","type":"title","text":"对军委关于军事系统向中央汇报工作问题的报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997"},{"id":"51c7140ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"军委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997"},{"id":"e4ccf01035","type":"paragraph","text":"上半年忙，下半年为妥。不要都准备，有四总、空、海即够，看情形定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997"},{"id":"7743e217fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997"},{"id":"00e8d61cea","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997"}],"page":{"id":"cafb5a2839","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"d03f040997","start":292,"end":292}}}},"__N_SSG":true}